title: 20 Minute Spin Class Workout (FAT BURNING INDOOR CYCLING!!)
description:
Best fat burning workouts can be found in our 90 day fitness program
http://athleanx.com/x/best-fat-burn

This 20 minute spin class workout is a great fat burning indoor cycling routine.  This spin class workout includes intervals of high intensity spinning followed by periods of lower intensity indoor cycling.  It’s a great idea to include indoor cycling class in your workout plan one to two days per week on days that you’re not lifting weights.

This 20 minute spinning workout will get your heart rate pumping and help you burn fat and calories.  You can do this indoor cycling workout at home if you’ve got a stationary or spinning bike, or it can be done in the gym.  You’ll need to adjust the resistance on your spinning bike to make sure you’re working harder during the high intensity intervals, and let up on the resistance a little bit during the lower intensity periods.

A 20 minute indoor cycling workout is the perfect amount  of time to give your metabolism a boost to help burn fat.  However too much cardio exercise can actually waste away at your muscle tone.  Make sure to keep spinning workouts to a maximum of 2 per week.

For all the best fat burning and strength training workouts, subscribe to our Youtube channel  https://www.youtube.com/user/womensworkouts
